ath of an Amazon Princess</span><hr size=1> Yakut looked up form her tears and she came to embrace Aly speaking a soft, &quot;Hi.&quot; but as Hippoyte came into sight the Queen came running to the comfort of her friend. Hippolyte was different from the rest of her friends, they had a connection through Otere that made their relationship special.<br>
